title: God Trended Me 3/16: New Jersey, Stock Market, Tom Brady, Penguins
itunes:title: God Trended Me 3/16: New Jersey, Stock Market, Tom Brady, Penguins
description:
On this very quarantined edition of God Trended Me Jack and Miles discuss New Jersey establishing a curfew, the Stock Market plummets as Trump reveals how long things may take to go back to normal, people are actually discussing where Tom Brady might be traded (or not traded), and some penguins are walking the grounds at the Chicago Aquarium.
